  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Support Executive (fresh graduate are welcome)",
  "description": "<p>Job Brief:</p><p><br /></p><p>We're seeking a motivated and enthusiastic Sales Support Executive to join our dynamic team! As a Sales Support Executive, you'll be the first point of contact for our customers, providing top-notch support and ensuring their satisfaction with our products and services. If you are a fresh graduate looking to kick-start your career in sales support, we would love to hear from you!</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Answer incoming calls and respond to customer inquiries in a cheerful and professional manner</li><li>Resolve customer complaints and issues promptly and efficiently</li><li>Support our sales team by processing orders, maintaining customer records, and providing necessary data and reports</li><li>Collaborate with the sales team to meet month-end goals</li><li>Provide administrative support to the sales team, including coordinating sales meetings and making travel arrangements</li><li>Create and issue sales tracking documentation as needed</li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>All fresh graduates are welcome.</li><li>Excellent verbal and written communication skills</li><li>Strong attention to detail and customer service skills</li><li>Ability to work independently with a high degree of accuracy and efficiency</li><li>Proficiency in MS Office (MS Word, Excel, PowerPoint)</li><li>Good work attitudes</li></ul>",
